    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2>洛南国依洛水而建，曾兴百年有余。<br><br>一场诡异又严重的瘟疫之后，洛南[异鬼]横行，所到之处，生者无几。[天一道]横空出世，惩处恶鬼，救万民于水火之中，短短十年间便权倾朝野，庙观开遍洛南。但乱世之中，各方势力的角逐、以及邪恶道士与异鬼的侵扰，致使民不聊生……<br>玩家将亲历不同的角色，解开缠绕在他们身上的因果执念，同时拨云散雾，探寻云安城下被掩埋十年的过往与秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/27be60d377065749d4920a514a578eab.poster.avif?t=1721790773\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/27be60d377065749d4920a514a578eab.webm?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/27be60d377065749d4920a514a578eab.mp4?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的卡牌玩法和规则</h2>参照中国的八卦风水学独创的八卦圆形牌场“浑元盘”，构成游戏两大核心规则的基础。<br><br>阴阳相冲，同阳充盈，每步都是一招致胜或反败为胜的手段。<br>独特的机制“化元”，阴阳互换，每个回合，或许能让你在陷入逆境之时扭转乾坤。<br>随着进度的推进逐渐扩充和构筑你的专属牌组。策略性地组合能力、功能各异的浑元牌、奇象牌将带来各种创意的玩法和惊人的效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/76432e380e4d219c8cbd9e7f3107be7f.poster.avif?t=1721790773\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/76432e380e4d219c8cbd9e7f3107be7f.webm?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/76432e380e4d219c8cbd9e7f3107be7f.mp4?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >志怪异谈的国风水墨世界</h2>以《聊斋志异》《搜神记》等中国传统神话精怪志异小说为蓝本创造的世界观，水墨古风的美术风格让你更沉浸在一个充满神鬼、怪谈以及荒诞的世界里。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/78e0c61d152a884c50e8bc6d07f6feb9.avif?t=1721790773\" width=600 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的游玩内容和剧情</h2>对战不同的敌人，甚至强大的BOSS，应对他们强大的阵法牌与符咒，杀出一条血路。<br><br>美貌老板娘开的神秘商店记得驻足停留，里面能够换取更多卡牌或功能强大的物品。<br>每张信物牌都构成主角身上的故事碎片，谜团将被逐渐解开。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/fe5429015f347e12b027ceb7d6482859.poster.avif?t=1721790773\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/fe5429015f347e12b027ceb7d6482859.webm?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/fe5429015f347e12b027ceb7d6482859.mp4?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亟待探索的地图和充满奇遇的冒险</h2>你将踏上迷雾笼罩的洛南国，在这片危险神秘的国土上自由探索，朝着真相前进。<br><br>每一次的旅途中，你所面临的选择都是不同的。每局游戏都能随机生成新的探索点，冒险之路充满了神奇与未知。<br>在一些特定区域中，可能遇到某些独特的奇遇造物或故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/b983a7ce915cc656cc7feed61a909b25.poster.avif?t=1721790773\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/b983a7ce915cc656cc7feed61a909b25.webm?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331080/extras/b983a7ce915cc656cc7feed61a909b25.mp4?t=1721790773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>目前游戏快速研发阶段，如果有想提出建议，欢迎进群讨论！<br>《浮生九还》玩家QQ交流群：574875317",
